{"tid":454594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［愛國愛黨］我想係西洋菜街 搞檔唱國歌","createTime":"2017-11-01T09:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T10:01:56.000Z","uid":73454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"127e1e37d690394bb5df61993520b47625d4a30b","tid":454594,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我見香港人對國家歸屬感不足，想藉著星期六日係旺角西洋菜街搞檔愛我中華之國歌唱起來，等大家為未來國歌法做好準備，好好學習如何唱得一首好歌。<br />\n<br />\n但最大難題係上下左右都充斥著廢老歌唱團技安式既歌聲，咁如果我播國歌時，佢地係隔離唱其他歌仲跳舞算唔算侮辱國歌，當我播起國歌時個aoe範圍又係點計算既呢？又如果佢地唔比我擺檔又算唔算犯左國歌法？<br />\n<br />\n真心求教"},{"pid":"e15a72b9d2859a68ccfd9dee8b7748da125e8e35","tid":454594,"uid":8000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"全日播國歌<br />\n佢地仲跳舞立即報黨處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001266e8298a337b4208e69d870e0ae704bf318c","tid":454594,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"留明支持 播行喇叭 Loop足一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e83759241d36ed58a42a38a866c2fa9715e22f","tid":454594,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"Aie大技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e703d5d78bfd11edd8f73e97b6f93fd8c456103","tid":454594,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Aoe<br />\n大技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}